LIBPCO INSTALLATION OVERVIEW

Quick Start - Linux
-------------------

Install CMake, the SiliconSoftware microEnable IV driver and the microEnable IV
Framegrabber runtime.

   $ mkdir build
   $ cd build
   $ cmake PATH_TO_SOURCE
   $ make
   $ make install

Disable the generation of the documentation by calling `ccmake
PATH_TO_BUILD_DIR` and changing WITH_DOCUMENTATION from ON to OFF.
